{{For|the tithe|Maaser Sheni}}
{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}
'''Ma'aser Sheni''' ([[Hebrew language|Hebrew]]: מעשר שני, lit. "[[Second tithe|Second Tithe]]") is the eighth tractate of ''[[Zeraim|Seder Zeraim]]'' ("Order of Seeds") of the ''[[Mishnah]]'' and of the ''[[Talmud]]''. It concerns the second tithe obligation as well as the laws of Revai.

